Elysium Earth Shipping Policy

Elysium Earth ("we" and "us") is the operator of (https://Elysium Earth.in/) ("Website"). By acing an order through this online website you will acknowledge the terms below. These policies are conducted to ensure both parties are aware of and agree upon these arrangements to mutually protect our customer's expectations and set expectations on our services.

1. General

Subject to stock availability. We try to maintain accurate stock counts on our website but from time to time, there may be a stock discrepancy and we will not be able to fulfill all your items at the same time of purchase. In this instance, we will take the order of available products for you, and contact you whether you would prefer to await restocking of your favorite product item or would you prefer to process a refund.

2. Shipment Processing Time

Elysium Earth’s all orders proceed within 2-3 business days. Orders are not shipped or delivered on weekends or holidays. If we are experiencing a high volume of orders, shipments may be held up by few days. ease wait and keep patience for additional days in transit for delivery. If there will be a significant delay in the shipment of your ordered product, we will contact you via email or telephone.

3. Shipping Costs

Shipping costs will be calculated during checkout based on weight, distance, dimensions, and destination of the purchased items in the order. Shipping payment will also be collected with the purchase, and the price will be the final price for shipping cost to the customer.

4. Returns

(Return Due To Change of Mind/Cancellation)

Elysium Earth's team will happily accept returns due to change of mind as long as a request to return is received by us within 7 days of receipt of the item and are returned to us in original packaging, unused, and can be resold condition. If an order has already been dispatched, ease refer to our refund policy.
Return shipping will be paid at the customer's expense and will be required to arrange their shipping. Once returns are received and accepted, refunds will be processed to our valuable customer's payment source. We will notify you once everything has been cometed by us through email. (Elysium Earth) will refund the value of the goods returned but will NOT refund the value of any shipping charges.

5. Delivery Terms
  • Transit Time in Domestic

    Generally, domestic shipments will be in transit for 2 - 7 days.

  • Transit time in International

    In general, orders shipped internationally are in transit for 5 - 24 days. This variation depends on the courier you have selected. We can offer a more specific estimate when you are choosing your courier at the checkout.

  • Change of Delivery Address

    Orders aced before (Time) GMT+5:30 will be dispatched the same day, otherwise, within the next business day.
    Elysium Earth's warehouse operates from Monday to Friday during standard business hours, except on national holidays and also at which time the warehouse will be closed. In these occurrences, we take steps to ensure shipment delays will be kept to a minimum.
    For a change of delivery address requests for your purchased items, we can change the address at any time before the order has been dispatched.

  • Exceed of Delivery Time

    If the delivery time has exceeded the predicted or estimated time, ease contact our team, so that we can conduct the action of investigation.

6. Tracking Notifications

After the dispatch, customers will receive a tracking link from that they will be able to follow the progress of their shipment based on the latest updates made available by the supplier.

  • Parcels Damaged In Transit

    If you find your ordered products are damaged in transit, if possible, please reject the parcel from the courier and get in touch with our customer service. And if the parcel hasn't been delivered to you or without you being present, please contact customer service as soon as possible.

7. Duties & Taxes
  • Sales Tax

    Sales tax has already been applied to the price of the products as displayed on the website.

  • Import Duties & Taxes

    Import duties and taxes for international shipments will be pre-paid, without any additional fees to be paid by the customer upon arrival in the destination country.

8. Insurance
  • Process for parcel damaged

    Our company will process a refund or replacement as soon as the courier has completed their investigation into the claim.

  • Process for parcel lost

    Our company will process a replacement or refund as soon as the courier has been investigated the parcel lost.

9. Customer service

For all the customer service inquiries,

Please email us at https://Elysium Earth.in/list.
